module.name: InterfaceBase
module.short: Provides a widget set appropriate to the operating system platform in use

element.name: TWidgetSet
element.short: TWidgetSet - a set of images and graphic tools for application programming, selected according to the operating system platform

descr.p: TWidgetSet - a set of images and graphic tools for application programming, selected according to the operating system platform
The appropriate set of widgets will be selected according to the operating system, either WinAPI for Microsoft Windows or LCL for most other systems

p.var: The declaration contains very few properties, but large numbers of very specific methods for interfacing with the operating system
